{
  "texts": [
    "We collect 341 groups in total.",
    "The interactions in various forum groups were also recorded, offering insights into their interests and engagement patterns.",
    "• Self-reported personality traits: Each user's self-reported MBTI/Enneagram type is crucial in aligning their social behaviors with specific personality traits.",
    "We here treat the personality traits as user labels.",
    "Besides MBTI and Enneagram types, part of these users also offer their BigFive personality types, which is another popular personality labeling system."
  ]
}